    "content": "\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n                     CHEERLEADER (Felix Jaehn Remix) - OMI\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nTabbed by: Guidedwhispers\r\nE-mail: guidedwhispers.my@gmail.com\r\n\r\n\r\nFairly easy song to play on the bass. All you need is the feel for the groove and the syncopation. \r\nSome parts of the song does not have bass, but just in case you wanna play it, I've tabbed it under \"EXTRAS\". \r\nThe notes basically follow the root note of the piano chords. \r\nOne word of caution, the form of the bass parts may seem identical and repetitive. \r\nHowever, there slight variations usually found in the 2nd and 4th bars of most bass phrases.\r\nThe time markers were referenced from the official video from \"Ultra Music\".\r\n\r\n\r\nTuning: Standard (EADG)\r\n\r\n[tab]EXTRAS\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-0-----7--5--0-----7--5--0-----7--5--0-----7--5--(continued to other parts)|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]PRE-CHORUS 1 (0:41)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-0--5--7--5--0--5--7--5----------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]CHORUS 1 (0:49)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-7-7--------------7-7-----------------7-7--------------7-7-----------------|\r\nE|-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0-0--7-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0---7--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]VERSE 2 (1:06)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-7-7--------------7-7-----------------7-7--------------7-7-----------------|\r\nE|-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0-0--7-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]PRE-CHORUS 2 (1:22)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-0--5--7--5--0--5--7--5----------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]CHORUS 2 (1:30)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-7-7--------------7-7-----------------7-7--------------7-7-----------------|\r\nE|-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0----7-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0-0--7-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]INTERLUDE (1:46)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-7-7--------------7-7-----------------7-7--------------7-7-----------------|\r\nE|-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0-0--7-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]PRE-CHORUS 3 (2:19)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-0--5--7--5--0--5--7--5--0--5--7--5--0--5--7--5----------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]CHORUS 3 (2:35)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-7-7--------------7-7-----------------7-7--------------7-7-----------------|\r\nE|-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0----7-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0-0--7-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]OUTRO (2:51)\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-7-7--------------7-7-----------------7-7----------------------------------|\r\nE|-----5--5-7-7-0-------5--5-7-7-0----7-----5--5-7-7-0-----------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n******************************************************************************\r\nEasy right?! :)\r\n******************************************************************************",
